### 測試 1: 建立一張成功訂單 (自取)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "測試員小明",
  "phone": "0912345678",
  "tireBrand": "Michelin",
  "tireSeries": "Pilot Sport 5",
  "tireSize": "225/40/R18",
  "quantity": 4,
  "installationOption": "NO_PICKUP"
}

### 測試 2: 建立一張失敗訂單 (選配送但沒填地址 -> 應該回傳 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "粗心的客戶",
  "phone": "0988777666",
  "tireBrand": "Bridgestone",
  "tireSeries": "Alenza",
  "tireSize": "235/55/R19",
  "quantity": 2,
  "installationOption": "NO_DELIVERY",
  "deliveryAddress": ""
}

### 測試 3: 查詢所有訂單
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders